-- This is auto-generated code
SELECT
    TOP 100 *
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://citylogisticsstorageprod.dfs.core.windows.net/synapse/Structured Data/OPS/stlmstrack.parquet/**',
        FORMAT = 'PARQUET'
    ) AS R 
--WHERE lms_track_waybillid = 12604864 OR lms_track_waybillid = 12604607
--WHERE lms_track_parcelid IN (309554922,309619875)
WHERE lms_track_parcelid = 299923348
--ORDER BY lms_track_opendt
ORDER BY lms_track_opendt 

SELECT
CASE WHEN lms_track_waybillid IS NULL THEN 'NULL' ELSE 'EXISTS' END AS CATEGORY
,EOMONTH(lms_track_opendt) as MonthVal
,COUNT(*) AS NUM_TRACKS
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://citylogisticsstorageprod.dfs.core.windows.net/synapse/Structured Data/OPS/stlmstrack.parquet/**',
        FORMAT = 'PARQUET'
    ) AS R
WHERE lms_track_tracktypeid = 6
AND lms_track_opendt >= '2023-01-01'
GROUP BY CASE WHEN lms_track_waybillid IS NULL THEN 'NULL' ELSE 'EXISTS' END
,EOMONTH(lms_track_opendt)

ORDER BY MonthVal, CATEGORY
